Hangman Game 🎯

A simple Hangman game built with Python as part of a programming task. This command-line game allows the user to guess letters of a randomly selected word, with a limited number of lives and ASCII-based visual feedback.

📁 Project Structure
- `main.py` – Main game logic
- `hangman_words.py` – Contains a list of words for the game
- `hangman_art.py` – Contains ASCII logo and hangman stages

🔧 Features
- Tracks correct and incorrect guesses
- Displays number of lives left
- Prevents duplicate guesses from affecting gameplay
- ASCII art for game stages and logo
